# Views/Modifiers Directory
# 
# This directory should contain custom SwiftUI view modifiers:
# - CardStyle.swift (consistent card styling)
# - LoadingOverlay.swift (loading state modifier)
# - ErrorAlert.swift (error presentation modifier)
# - KeyboardAdaptive.swift (keyboard avoidance)
# - Shimmer.swift (skeleton loading effect)
# - ConditionalModifier.swift (conditional styling)
# - DeviceSpecific.swift (iPad vs iPhone modifiers)
# - AccessibilityModifiers.swift (accessibility enhancements)
# 
# View modifiers enable consistent styling and behavior
# across the app while keeping views clean and focused